tested with MacOS with Homebrew
$brew install sbt  (0.13)
$brew install scala (2.10.3)

tested with vanilla Debian stable with Vagrant:
$apt-get install scala (2.9.10)
$wget http://repo.scala-sbt.org/scalasbt/sbt-native-packages/org/scala-sbt/sbt/0.13.0/sbt.deb
$dpkg -i sbt.deb (0.13)
If the image has very little memory SBT might fail.. use the -mem flag to reduce memory

RUN APP:
$ sbt run

RUN TESTS:
Bundled with specs2
$ sbt test

PACKAGE WITH ALL DEPENDENCIES:
Bundled from https://github.com/sbt/sbt-assembly
$ sbt assembly

RUN PACKAGE WITH SCALA/JVM:
$ cd target/scala-2.10/
$ scala Drawing-assembly-0.1-SNAPSHOT.jar
or...
$ java -jar Drawing-assembly-0.1-SNAPSHOT.jar